org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce

接口 MRConfig

  • 所有已知子接口:
    JTConfig, TTConfig

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public interface MRConfig
    Place holder for cluster level configuration keys. The keys should have "mapreduce.cluster." as the prefix.
